    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1881-02-19T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1881-02-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="218" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d218">
                <head>No. 214.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Evarts</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Noyes</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1881-02-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">February</hi> 19,
                            1881</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>If decree has issued prohibiting importation of American meats, present
                        regret of this government, and protest firmly if it seems appropriate to do
                        so.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>EVARTS.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
